latestIgtvVideos.title: How and why olaplex?
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey friends,
I recently got Olaplex done and I feel it will help everyone who have damaged their hair by continuously coloring, using heating tools and chemical treatments. 
Olaplex works on a molecular level to seek out broken bonds that are caused by chemical , thermal and mechanical damage. 
I hope you guys give it a try to share your reviews with me :) Raa by Ritika

Location : 
2/519 vijay khand Gomti Nagar lucknow

latestPosts.caption:
While shopping in Guanghzou, China I stumbled up on a lot of WOW colour stores, which is basically Sephora of asian countries and I had already seen @flowerknows_global  before, and I knew I had to buy their products, but oh my God, the packaging  the design were so feminine and dreamy, I could not resist. 
Also they are bang on good.
I wanted to buy one of the eye palattes which was crazy, but it was out of stock. Maybe next time. @flowerknows_global if you’re watching this, send me 👀
.
.
#makeup #blush #liquidblush #makeupgoals #flowerknows
